trans-unit.source: Defines a print job in detail.
trans-unit.target: Definerer en utskriftsjobben i detalj.

trans-unit.source: This class has no public constructor.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen, har ingen offentlig konstruktør.

trans-unit.source: To get a reference to a PrintSystemJobInfo object, use the static <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Get%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method or one of the following <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> instance methods: <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.GetJob%2A>, <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.GetPrintJobInfoCollection%2A>, or <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AddJob%2A>.
trans-unit.target: For å hente en referanse til et PrintSystemJobInfo-objekt, kan du bruke statiske <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Get%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden eller én av følgende <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>serverforekomsten metoder: <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.GetJob%2A>, <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.GetPrintJobInfoCollection%2A>, eller <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AddJob%2A>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AddJob%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.GetPrintJobInfoCollection%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.GetJob%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> </xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Get%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Many print job properties, such as whether a job is completed, must be passed from the printer to the PrintSystemJobInfo object before your application reads the corresponding property (<xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.IsCompleted%2A>).
trans-unit.target: Mange utskriftsjobben egenskaper, for eksempel om en jobb er fullført, må få tilsendt fra skriveren til PrintSystemJobInfo objektet før programmet leser den tilsvarende egenskapen (<xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.IsCompleted%2A>).</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.IsCompleted%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Refresh%2A> method provides this functionality.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Refresh%2A>metoden gir denne funksjonaliteten.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Refresh%2A>

trans-unit.source: Similarly, when your application changes the value of the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.JobName%2A> property, the change must be written to the print queue utility on the computer.
trans-unit.target: På samme måte når programmet endrer verdien for den <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.JobName%2A>egenskapen endringen må være skrevet til køen-verktøyet på datamaskinen.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.JobName%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Commit%2A> method provides this functionality.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Commit%2A>metoden gir denne funksjonaliteten.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Commit%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you derive a class from PrintSystemJobInfo that has additional writable properties, then you must implement an override of the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Refresh%2A> and <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Commit%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du avledet en klasse fra PrintSystemJobInfo som har flere skrivbar egenskaper og deretter må du implementere en overstyring av den <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Refresh%2A>og <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Commit%2A>metoder.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Commit%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Refresh%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!CAUTION] > Classes within the <xref:System.Printing> namespace are not supported for use within a Windows service or ASP.NET application or service.
trans-unit.target: > [!CAUTION] > Klasser i den <xref:System.Printing>navneområdet støttes ikke for bruk i en Windows ASP.NET-program eller tjeneste.</xref:System.Printing>

trans-unit.source: Attempting to use these classes from within one of these application types may produce unexpected problems, such as diminished service performance and run-time exceptions.
trans-unit.target: Forsøk på å bruke disse klassene fra i ett av disse programtyper kan føre til uventede problemer, for eksempel dårligere tjeneste ytelse og kjøretid unntak.

trans-unit.source: If you want to print from a Windows Forms application, see the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing> namespace.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil skrive ut fra en Windows Forms-program, kan du se den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing>navneområde.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing>

trans-unit.source: Cancels the print job.
trans-unit.target: Avbryter utskriftsjobben.

trans-unit.source: Writes any changes to the properties of the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo"></xref> object to the actual print job that the object represents.
trans-unit.target: Skriver ingen endringer i egenskapene til det <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo"> </xref> -objekt til faktiske utskriftsjobben som representerer objektet.

trans-unit.source: Only the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.JobName%2A> property is writable.
trans-unit.target: Bare den <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.JobName%2A>egenskapen er skrivbar.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.JobName%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you derive a class from <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> that has additional writable properties, you must override the Commit and <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Refresh%2A> methods with implementations of your own.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du avledet en klasse fra <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>med skrivbar tilleggsegenskaper, må du overstyre transaksjonen og <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Refresh%2A>metoder med implementeringer av dine egne.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Refresh%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources that are used by the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo"></xref> and optionally, releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Frigir uforvaltede ressursene som brukes av den <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo"> </xref> og eventuelt frigir administrerte ressurser.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.

trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om utskriftsjobben er blokkert, og derfor ikke ut.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the print job is blocked; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis utskriftsjobben blokkeres; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the print job is finished.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om utskriftsjobben er fullført.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the print job, which is represented by the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo"></xref> object, was deleted from the print queue.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om utskriftsjobben, som er representert av den <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo"> </xref> objekt, ble slettet fra køen.

trans-unit.source: It may seem paradoxical at first that an object can report its own status as deleted, but keep in mind that the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> object only *represents* a real print job.
trans-unit.target: Det kan virke paradoxical først et objekt kan rapportere egenhånd status slettet, men husk å huske at den <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>objekt bare *representerer* real utskriftsjobben.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>

trans-unit.source: Deleting the latter from its print queue does not automatically dispose of the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> object in your application.
trans-unit.target: Sletting av det siste fra køen ikke automatisk fjerne det <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>objektet i applikasjonen.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>

trans-unit.source: Similarly, the object is not removed from any <xref:System.Printing.PrintJobInfoCollection> that was created before the print job it represents was deleted.
trans-unit.target: På samme måte objektet blir ikke fjernet fra alle <xref:System.Printing.PrintJobInfoCollection>som ble opprettet før utskriftsjobben den representerer ble slettet.</xref:System.Printing.PrintJobInfoCollection>

trans-unit.source: For example, if the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.GetPrintJobInfoCollection%2A> method is run before the print job was deleted, the returned collection will include a <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> object that represents the print job.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel hvis den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.GetPrintJobInfoCollection%2A>metoden kjøres før utskriftsjobben ble slettet, returnerte samlingen inkluderer en <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>objektet som representerer utskriftsjobben.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.GetPrintJobInfoCollection%2A>

trans-unit.source: This object is not removed from the collection when the print job is deleted.
trans-unit.target: Dette objektet er ikke fjernes fra samlingen når utskriftsjobben er slettet.

trans-unit.source: But if <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.GetPrintJobInfoCollection%2A> is then run again, the returned collection will have no members that represent the deleted print jobs.
trans-unit.target: Men hvis <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.GetPrintJobInfoCollection%2A>deretter kjøres på nytt, den returnerte samlingen har ingen medlemmer som representerer slettet jobbene.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.GetPrintJobInfoCollection%2A>

trans-unit.source: Contrast restarting with using the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Resume%2A> method, which resumes a job at the point it was paused.
trans-unit.target: Kontrast starte med å bruke den <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Resume%2A>metoden som gjenopptar en jobb på stedet den ble stoppet midlertidig.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Resume%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets the identification number for the print job.
trans-unit.target: Henter ID-nummer for utskriftsjobben.

trans-unit.source: Which numbering system is used is determined by the operating system of the print server and whether the print server is a computer or a print server appliance.
trans-unit.target: Brukes som nummerering systemet er avhengig av operativsystemet på serveren og om serveren er en datamaskin eller på en serveren utstyr.

trans-unit.source: For example, the operating system for [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_whistler](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] determines the numbering in this way: when a print server is turned on, if all its print queues are empty, the first print job submitted on the server by any user and to any queue is assigned ID number 2.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel operativsystemet for [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_whistler](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] bestemmer nummereringen på denne måten: når en trykt server er aktivert, hvis alle de tilhørende trykt køene er tomme, første utskriftsjobben inn på serveren av en bruker og kø er tilordnet 2-IDen.

trans-unit.source: Each subsequent job on the server is assigned a number that is one greater than the previous print job on that server.
trans-unit.target: Hvert etterfølgende jobb på serveren er tilordnet til et tall som er en større enn den forrige utskriftsjobben på denne serveren.

trans-unit.source: The print queue for the print job has no effect on its number: if jobs are sent to QueueA, QueueB, and QueueA, in that order, then QueueA has jobs 2 and 4, and QueueB has job 3.
trans-unit.target: Køen for utskriftsjobben har ingen innvirkning på nummeret: Hvis jobber sendes til QueueA, QueueB og QueueA, i denne rekkefølgen og QueueA har jobber 2 og 4, og QueueB har jobben 3.

trans-unit.source: After a job is assigned a number, the number never changes, even if other jobs finish printing or are canceled, or if the server is restarted.
trans-unit.target: Når en jobb er tilordnet et tall, endres ikke nummeret, selv om andre jobber fullføre utskrift eller avbrytes, eller hvis serveren er startet på nytt.

trans-unit.source: If there are already jobs in one or more queues when the server is restarted, the first new job is assigned a number that is one greater than the highest numbered job that was in the queue when the server started.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det finnes allerede jobber i én eller flere køer når serveren er startet på nytt, den første nye jobben er tilordnet et tall som er en større enn den høyeste nummererte jobben som var i køen når serveren er startet.

trans-unit.source: However, until it restarts, a print server does not reuse a number.
trans-unit.target: Men før den startes på nytt, en serveren på nytt. et tall.

trans-unit.source: Even if the highest numbered job is canceled before it is printed, the next job gets a number that is one higher.
trans-unit.target: Selv om den høyeste nummererte jobben er avbrutt før den skrives, henter et tall som er en høyere neste jobb.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Int32> that identifies the print job.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Int32>som identifiserer utskriftsjobben.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a name for the print job.

trans-unit.source: Gets the current status of the print job.

trans-unit.source: This method gives you a means to avoid individually checking each of the status properties, such as <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.IsPrinting%2A> and <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.IsPaused%2A>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a reference to the <xref:System.IO.Stream> of the print job.

trans-unit.source: Starting with the .NET Framework 4.5 on Windows 8 and later versions of the operating system, data written to this stream must be in XPS format as a package stream.
trans-unit.target: Starter med .NET Framework 4.5 på Windows 8 og nyere versjoner av operativsystemet, må data som skrives til denne dataflyten være i XPS-format som en pakke-dataflyt.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.IO.Stream> that contains the print job.

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of pages in the print job.
trans-unit.target: Henter antallet sider i utskriftsjobben.

trans-unit.source: A page is one side of a sheet of paper or other print media.
trans-unit.target: En side er ene siden av et ark eller andre Skriv ut mediet.

trans-unit.source: The following table shows how the value of this property, and the number of sheets used, is affected by whether the print job calls for two-sided printing (duplexing), whether it calls for multiple pages-per-sheet, or whether it calls for both.
trans-unit.target: Tabellen nedenfor viser hvordan verdien for denne egenskapen og hvor mange ark som er brukt, påvirkes av om utskriftsjobben kaller for begge sider utskrift (dupleksing), om kaller for flere sider per blad eller om kaller for begge.

trans-unit.source: How duplexing and multipage printing affect printing |Duplexing|Pages per sheet|Value of NumberOfPages|Number of physical sheets of paper| |---------------|---------------------|----------------------------|----------------------------------------| |No|1|Identical to the number of pages in the document.|Identical to the number of pages in the document.| |Yes|1|Identical to the number of pages in the document.|Document pages ÷ 2 (rounded up).| |No|Multiple|Document pages ÷ Pages per sheet (rounded up).|Document pages ÷ Pages per sheet (rounded up).| |Yes|Multiple|Document pages ÷ Pages per sheet (rounded up).|[Document pages ÷ Pages per sheet] ÷ 2 (rounded up).|
trans-unit.target: Hvordan dupleksing og med flere sider utskrift påvirker utskrift | Dupleksing | Sider per ark | Verdien for NumberOfPages | Antall fysisk ark | |---------------|---------------------|----------------------------|----------------------------------------| | Ikke | 1 | Identiske antallet sider i dokumentet. | Identiske antallet sider i dokumentet. | | Ja | 1 | Identiske antallet sider i dokumentet. | Dokumentere sider ÷ 2 (avrundet oppover). | | Ikke | Flere | Dokumentet sider ÷ sider per ark (avrundet oppover). | Dokumentet sider ÷ sider per ark (avrundet oppover). | | Ja | Flere | Dokumentet sider ÷ sider per ark (avrundet oppover). | [Dokumentet sider ÷ sider per ark] ÷ 2 (avrundet oppover). |

trans-unit.source: Halts printing of the job until <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Resume*> runs.
trans-unit.target: Stanser utskrift jobbens før <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Resume*>kjører.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Resume*>

trans-unit.source: If another job is in the queue, it begins printing when the current job is paused.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en annen jobb i køen, begynner utskrift når gjeldende jobb er midlertidig stanset.

trans-unit.source: The hosting <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> also has <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Pause%2A> and <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Resume%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: Den drifter <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>har også <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Pause%2A>og <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Resume%2A>metoder.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Resume%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Pause%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>

trans-unit.source: If the print queue is paused, resuming an individual job does not cause that job to resume printing.
trans-unit.target: Hvis køen er satt på pause, gjenopptar en enkelt jobb fører ikke til denne jobben å gjenoppta utskrift.

trans-unit.source: Gets the print job's place in the print queue.
trans-unit.target: Henter den utskriftsjobben sted i køen.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Int32> that states the print job's place in the queue.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Int32>som angir den utskriftsjobben sted i køen.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: Gets a non-numerical expression that represents the priority of the print job relative to other jobs in the print queue.
trans-unit.target: Henter en ikke-numerisk uttrykk som representerer prioriteten for utskriftsjobben i forhold til andre jobber i køen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Printing.PrintJobPriority"></xref> that represents the priority of the print job as <xref href="System.Printing.PrintJobPriority"></xref>, <xref href="System.Printing.PrintJobPriority"></xref>, <xref href="System.Printing.PrintJobPriority"></xref>, or <xref href="System.Printing.PrintJobPriority"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Printing.PrintJobPriority"></xref> that represents the priority of the print job as <xref href="System.Printing.PrintJobPriority"></xref>, <xref href="System.Printing.PrintJobPriority"></xref>, <xref href="System.Printing.PrintJobPriority"></xref>, or <xref href="System.Printing.PrintJobPriority"></xref>.

trans-unit.source: Updates the properties of the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo"></xref> object so that their values match the values of the actual print job that the object represents.
trans-unit.target: Oppdaterer egenskapene for den <xref href="System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo"> </xref> objektet slik at verdiene samsvarer med verdiene i den faktiske utskriftsjobben objektet representerer.

trans-unit.source: Any changes that you make to the properties of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> object must be written to the actual print job by using the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Commit%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Endringer du gjør egenskaper for en <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>objektet må skrives til faktiske utskriftsjobben ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Commit%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Commit%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>

trans-unit.source: Any changes that you have not committed are lost when the Refresh method runs.
trans-unit.target: Endringer du ikke har utført går tapt når metoden oppdateringen kjører.

trans-unit.source: If you derive a class from <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> that has additional properties, then you must override the Refresh method with an implementation of your own.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du avledet en klasse fra <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>som har flere egenskaper og deretter må du overstyre metoden oppdatering med implementering av dine egne.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>

trans-unit.source: Restarts a print job from the beginning.
trans-unit.target: Starter utskriftsjobben fra begynnelsen.

trans-unit.source: Optionally, you can use the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Resume%2A> method, which restarts a paused print job, starting at the point it was paused.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også bruke den <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Resume%2A>metode som starter en midlertidig stanset utskriftsjobben som starter ved punkt den ble stoppet midlertidig.</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Resume%2A>

trans-unit.source: Resumes the printing of a paused print job.
trans-unit.target: Gjenopptar utskrift av en midlertidig stanset utskriftsjobben.

trans-unit.source: The hosting <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> also has <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Pause%2A> and <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Resume%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: Den drifter <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>har også <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Pause%2A>og <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Resume%2A>metoder.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Resume%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Pause%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>

trans-unit.source: If the print queue is paused, resuming an individual job does not resume the printing of the print job.
trans-unit.target: Hvis køen er satt på pause, starter gjenopptar en individuelle jobb ikke utskrift av utskriftsjobben.

trans-unit.source: Gets the earliest time of day, expressed as the number of minutes after midnight Coordinated Universal Time (UTC) (also called Greenwich Mean Time [GMT]), that the print job can begin printing.
trans-unit.target: Henter det tidligste klokkeslettet, uttrykt som antall minutter etter midnatt Coordinated Universal Time (UTC) (også kalt Greenwich mellomtiden [GMT]), at utskriftsjobben kan begynne utskrift.

trans-unit.source: This value is propagated to each <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> object from the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.StartTimeOfDay%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property of the hosting <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> at the time the job enters the queue.
trans-unit.target: Denne verdien er overført til hver <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>objektet fra den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.StartTimeOfDay%2A?displayProperty=fullName>for den drifter <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>da jobben går inn i køen.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.StartTimeOfDay%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.StartTimeOfDay%2A?displayProperty=fullName> is changed, then any StartTimeOfDay value that is earlier than <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.StartTimeOfDay%2A?displayProperty=fullName> is changed to the value of <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.StartTimeOfDay%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.StartTimeOfDay%2A?displayProperty=fullName>endres, deretter en StartTimeOfDay verdi som er eldre enn <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.StartTimeOfDay%2A?displayProperty=fullName>endres til verdien for <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.StartTimeOfDay%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.StartTimeOfDay%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.StartTimeOfDay%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.StartTimeOfDay%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: After the job is added to the queue, it can be given a new StartTimeOfDay value through the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_win](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)], provided that it is not earlier than <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.StartTimeOfDay%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Når jobben er lagt til køen, den kan få en ny StartTimeOfDay-verdi i den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_win](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)], forutsatt at det ikke er tidligere enn <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.StartTimeOfDay%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.StartTimeOfDay%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If you are not in the UTC time zone, you must add or subtract multiples of 60 to get the correct time for your time zone.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du ikke er i UTC-tidssone, må du legge til eller trekke multiplum av 60 å hente riktig tid for tidssone.

trans-unit.source: For example, if you are in the Pacific Time Zone of North America and daylight savings time is not in effect, then your local time is 8 hours earlier than UTC.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel hvis du er i det Stillehavskysten sone i Nord-Amerika og sommertid klokkeslettet er ikke i kraft, og lokal tid er eldre enn UTC 8 timer.

trans-unit.source: If StartTimeOfDay returns 960, that means 16:00 (4:00 PM) in UTC (because 960/60 = 16).
trans-unit.target: Hvis StartTimeOfDay returnerer 960, som betyr 16:00 (4:00 PM) i UTC (fordi 960/60 = 16).

trans-unit.source: To convert this to Pacific Time, you must subtract 480 (= 8 * 60) minutes.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil konvertere denne til Stillehavskysten, må du trekke 480 (= 8 * 60) minutter.

trans-unit.source: You also must remember that time rolls over to zero after 24 hours (that is; after the 1439th minute).
trans-unit.target: Også må du huske som tid ruller til null etter 24 timer (det vil si; etter 1439th minutt).

trans-unit.source: If StartTimeOfDay returns 120, that means 2:00 AM in UTC.
trans-unit.target: Hvis StartTimeOfDay returnerer 120, som betyr at 2:00 AM i UTC.

trans-unit.source: To convert this to Pacific Time, you must subtract 480 minutes, which results in -360.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil konvertere denne til Stillehavskysten, må du trekke 480 minutter som fører til-360.

trans-unit.source: To get a positive value that has meaning, add the negative number to the total minutes in a day, 1440, resulting in a final value of 1080 (6:00 PM) Pacific Time.
trans-unit.target: Legg til negativt tall Totalt antall minutter i en dag, 1440, noe som førte til den endelige verdien Stillehavskysten 1080 (6:00 PM) for å få en positiv verdi som har betydning.

trans-unit.source: See <xref:System.TimeZone>, <xref:System.TimeSpan>, and <xref:System.DateTime> for methods that help make time-zone adjustments.
trans-unit.target: Se <xref:System.TimeZone>, <xref:System.TimeSpan>, og <xref:System.DateTime>for metoder som bidrar til å justere tidssone.</xref:System.DateTime> </xref:System.TimeSpan> </xref:System.TimeZone>

trans-unit.source: If the printer is always available, then this property returns 0 in all time zones.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det er alltid tilgjengelig, returnerer egenskapen 0 i alle tidssoner.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Int32> specifying the earliest possible start time for the print job, expressed as the number of minutes after midnight (UTC).

trans-unit.source: Gets the last time of day, expressed as the number of minutes after midnight Coordinated Universal Time (UTC) (also called Greenwich Mean Time [GMT]), that the print job can begin printing.
trans-unit.target: Henter det siste klokkeslettet, uttrykt som antall minutter etter midnatt Coordinated Universal Time (UTC) (også kalt Greenwich mellomtiden [GMT]), at utskriftsjobben kan begynne utskrift.

trans-unit.source: This value is propagated to each <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> object from the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.UntilTimeOfDay%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property of the hosting <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> at the time the job enters the queue.

trans-unit.target: Hvis <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.UntilTimeOfDay%2A?displayProperty=fullName>endres, deretter en UntilTimeOfDay verdi som er nyere enn <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.UntilTimeOfDay%2A?displayProperty=fullName>endres til verdien for <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.UntilTimeOfDay%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.UntilTimeOfDay%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.UntilTimeOfDay%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.UntilTimeOfDay%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: After the job is added to the queue, it can be given a new UntilTimeOfDay value through the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_win](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)], provided that it is not later than <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.UntilTimeOfDay%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
